text: Ingenbohl is a municipality in Schwyz District in the canton of Schwyz in Switzerland. It is located along the Lake Lucerne. == Villages == The municipality consists of the village of Ingenbohl and the hamlets of Brunnen, Wilen, Schränggigen and Unterschönenbuch. == References == == Other websites == * Official website Category:Municipalities in Schwyz District
title: Ingenbohl
